<exercise><statement><p>
      Find the
      
          y-intercepts
        
      for each of the following equations.
    </p><ul><li><m> -3 \, x - 3 \, y = \left(-4\right) </m></li><li><m> -3 \, x + 4 \, y = \left(-3\right) </m></li></ul></statement><answer><ul><li><m> \frac{4}{3} </m></li><li><m> -\frac{3}{4} </m></li></ul></answer></exercise>
